Former African National Congress Youth League (ANCYL) Secretary General Sindiso Magaqa has been shot. According to reports Magaqa and other two ANC members are in hospital after they were attacked and shot at Umzimkhulu, Kwazulu-Natal.The trio have been hospitalised and receiving medical treatment. ANC KZN Provincial Spokesperson Mdumiseni Ntuli confirmed the attack on their members. All three members were shot at around 6 pm at one of the local shops at Umzimkhulu. They are receiving medical attention in one of the hospitals, said Ntuli.Ntuli said the motive of the shooting is still unclear at this time.